import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-tab1', templateUrl: 'tab1.page.html', styleUrls: ['tab1.page.scss'] }) export class Tab1Page { constructor() {} } Inicio

Welcome to Ionic!

This starter project comes with simple tabs-based layout for apps that are going to primarily use a Tabbed UI.

Take a look at the src/pages/ directory to add or change tabs, update any existing page or create new pages.
